            "title": "直言不諱的代價：埃克森美孚CEO坦言委內瑞拉「不宜投資」 引特朗普不悅",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"直言不諱的代價：埃克森美孚CEO坦言委內瑞拉「不宜投資」 引特朗普不悅\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fG1G4fX45s0mYcS4GF3vjQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/c583f6a0-f082-11f0-bebe-c94cd8c2c3a7\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">直言不諱的代價：埃克森美孚CEO坦言委內瑞拉「不宜投資」 引特朗普不悅</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%9B%B4%E8%A8%80%E4%B8%8D%E8%AB%B1%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%A3%E5%83%B9-%E5%9F%83%E5%85%8B%E6%A3%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%AD%9Aceo%E5%9D%A6%E8%A8%80%E5%A7%94%E5%85%A7%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89-%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87-%E5%BC%95%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E4%B8%8D%E6%82%85-113918543.html",
