        {
            "title": "美國小企業樂觀情緒小幅上升 因經濟前景樂觀預期增強",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國12月小企業主信心指數連續第二個月上升，主要源於對經濟前景的樂觀預期增強。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">全美獨立企業聯合會(NFIB)周二公佈的數據顯示，樂觀指數上升0.5點至99.5，創四個月高點。構成該指數的10個分項指標中，有兩個上升，三個下降，五個持平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">淨24%的企業主表示預期未來六個月經營狀況將改善，這是整體指數上升的主要驅動力。該比例較11月上升9個百分點，但僅是自7月以來的首次上升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時，提高平均售價的企業淨占比下降4個百分點至30%。儘管該數據仍遠高於歷史均值（淨占比13%），但表明通膨壓力有所緩解。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4a155870-0b00-34d1-94f1-a969a2de6f63-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過，在11月觸及十個月高點後，企業對銷售成長的預期下降5個點。增加雇員的計畫也出現下滑。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著樂觀情緒回升，該組織的不確定性指數下降7點，降至2024年6月以來最低水平。稅收被列為小企業面臨的首要問題，其次是勞動力質量問題。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Small-Business Optimism Edges Higher on Economic Outlook</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E6%A8%82%E8%A7%80%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92%E5%B0%8F%E5%B9%85%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87-%E5%9B%A0%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%89%8D%E6%99%AF%E6%A8%82%E8%A7%80%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%B7-121821517.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-13 21:20:54",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國施壓不斷加劇 兩年前被伊朗扣押的一艘油輪似乎已經獲釋",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 兩年前被伊朗扣押的一艘油輪近日在阿曼海岸附近被拍到，暗示在美國對伊朗施壓不斷加劇的背景下，德黑蘭方面可能已釋放該船。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據專業船舶追蹤機構TankerTrackers.com稱，這艘名為「St Nikolas」號的油輪於2024年1月被扣押，伊朗當時稱此舉是對美國「竊取」伊朗石油的報復。該機構通過衛星圖像等工具追蹤包括伊朗附近船舶在內的航運動態。數據顯示該船最近出現在阿曼海岸Sohar錨地以北海域。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0612f4d5-fc04-353d-bf73-2bb3085977ce-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗外交部及該船管理方（海事數據庫Equasis顯示為總部在雅典的Empire Navigation）未立即回應電話及郵件置評請求。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">活動人士稱，過去兩周伊朗國內抗議活動持續動盪，已造成600多人死亡。美國總統唐納德·川普威脅將干預伊朗局勢，阻止該國政府的強力鎮壓。川普周一晚間宣布對任何「與德黑蘭做生意」的國家徵收25%關稅，數小時前他剛表示伊朗已就談判與美國進行接觸。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Iran Appears to Free Oil Tanker Seized in 2024 Over US Tensions</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%96%BD%E5%A3%93%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%B7%E5%8A%A0%E5%8A%87-%E5%85%A9%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E8%A2%AB%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%89%A3%E6%8A%BC%E7%9A%84-%E8%89%98%E6%B2%B9%E8%BC%AA%E4%BC%BC%E4%B9%8E%E5%B7%B2%E7%B6%93%E7%8D%B2%E9%87%8B-101909366.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-13 18:56:04",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "兆易創新香港上市首日飆升54% 此前通過IPO融資46.8億港元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 兆易創新在香港上市首日大漲，凸顯投資者對中國人工智能相關股票的興趣濃厚。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這是近來在香港上市的第二家半導體公司，該股周二在香港一度飆升54%，至248.80港元。該公司此前在股票發行交易中融資46.8億港元（6億美元），每股發行價為162港元，面向散戶投資者部分獲得542倍認購。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">兆易創新在香港首次亮相之際，正值內存晶片價格因供應短缺而上漲，全球生產商競相滿足人工智能領域日益成長的需求。該公司也加入了中國科技企業上市的浪潮，北京方面大力扶持本土企業，以與輝達和美光科技等巨頭展開競爭。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-79d44368-7a89-3970-9513-f36d7d888b95-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6omFRZvs73cTo4NTBapIsw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/245ed25b65a3a632c6909c0d01c688c4\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題GigaDevice Jumps 54% in Hong Kong After $600 Million Listing</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%86%E6%98%93%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82%E9%A6%96%E6%97%A5%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%8754-%E6%AD%A4%E5%89%8D%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8Eipo%E8%9E%8D%E8%B3%8746-8%E5%84%84%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83-015957460.html",
